insert into sfcx_xqxxhzb (tjrq,gsid,glcid,grs,xq,grnd,rwnd,
rwmj,gnmj,tgmj,dwmj,rwhs,gnhs,tghs,dwhs,sjys,yis,qf)
select ?,
jg.fgsbh gsid,jg.glcbh glcid,ys.grs,ys.xq,ys.grnd,yh.rwnd,
nvl(sum(case when ys.yrzt<>'退网' then ys.mjyl end),0) rwmj,
nvl(sum(case when ys.yrzt='正常' then ys.mjyl end),0) gnmj,
nvl(sum(case when ys.yrzt in ('报停','强停','永久停供') then ys.mjyl end),0) tgmj,
nvl(sum(case when ys.yrzt = '退网' then yh.sfmj end),0) dwmj,
count(distinct case when ys.yrzt<>'退网' then ys.yh end) rwhs,
count(distinct case when ys.yrzt='正常' then ys.yh end) gnhs,
count(distinct case when ys.yrzt in ('报停','强停','永久停供') then ys.yh end) tghs,
count(distinct case when ys.yrzt = '退网' then ys.yh end) dwhs,
nvl(sum(ys.sjys),0) sjys,
nvl(sum(ys.yis),0) yis,
nvl(sum(case when ys.jhys-nvl(ys.jm,0)-nvl(ys.youh,0)-nvl(ys.ml,0)-nvl(ys.yis,0)>0
then ys.jhys-nvl(ys.jm,0)-nvl(ys.youh,0)-nvl(ys.ml,0)-nvl(ys.yis,0) else 0 end),0) qf
from sfys_ys ys
inner join sfyh_yh yh on ys.yh=yh.id
inner join v_zzjg jg on yh.grs=jg.jgbh
inner join sfyh_xq xq on yh.xq=xq.id
group by jg.fgsbh,jg.glcbh,ys.grs,ys.xq,ys.grnd,yh.rwnd
